- Desmond Hume就是被我扔进这口井里去的  - 啊!
- This is the well I threw Desmond Hume into.  - Aah!

9
00:00:27,180 --> 00:00:29,650
- 貌似有人帮他逃了出来  - 不 Ben 是有人帮忙把我弄了出来
- Looks like someone helped him out.  - No, Ben, someone helped me out.

10
00:00:29,650 --> 00:00:30,800
我要找到Desmond
I'm gonna find Desmond.

11
00:00:30,880 --> 00:00:35,230
等我找到他后 我就毁了这个岛
And when I do, I'm gonna destroy the island.

12
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:38,370
前几天有一场交通肇事逃逸事故
There was a hit-and-run a few days ago

13
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:39,840
地点是华盛顿Tustin中学
at Washington Tustin high school.

14
00:00:41,290 --> 00:00:42,990
- 然后?  - 我就是嫌犯
- Yeah?  - I'm the suspect.

15
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:47,330
下午好 你今天过得如何?
Good afternoon. And how are you doing today?

16
00:00:47,990 --> 00:00:48,650
再好不过了
Terrific.

17
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:50,690
是时候走人了
I think it's time to leave.

18
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:55,370
你跟着他 你跟着我
You're with him, and you're with me.

19
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:57,490
我们去听音乐会
We are going to a concert.

20
00:00:58,910 --> 00:00:59,490
走吧
Let's go.

21
00:01:20,510 --> 00:01:24,320

大洋航空

22
