大洋航空

23
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:24,880

大洋航空

24
00:03:40,410 --> 00:03:41,590

遗体

25
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:43,940
- 需要人签收么?  - 你是这里的员工?
- Do you need somebody to sign for that?  - You work here?

26
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,510
如假包换 伙计
I do indeed, brother.

27
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,270
你是牧师 还是其他啥的?
You a priest or somethin'?

28
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:51,490
我不是牧师
Or something.

29
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:56,380
介意把东西运到那后面去么?
Do you mind taking it around the back there?

30
00:03:56,980 --> 00:03:58,150
没问题 我这就运过去
Yeah, sure. You got it.

31
00:04:09,410 --> 00:04:11,010
运到那边就好 谢谢
Just around there. Thank you.

32
00:04:24,010 --> 00:04:24,580
谁去世了?
Who died?

33
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:28,770
一个名叫Christian Shephard的男子
A man named Christian Shephard.

34
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:33,220
"Christian Shephard"吗?
"Christian Shephard"?

35
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:34,260
真的?
Seriously?

36
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:36,710
真的
Seriously.

37
00:04:39,970 --> 00:04:40,520
你朋友?
Friend of yours?

38
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:43,840
不算吧
Not exactly.

39
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,190
等... 等会儿
H... hang on a second.

40
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:48,590
你带我越狱 让我穿上这件礼服
You bust me out of jail and make me put on this dress

41
00:04:48,850 --> 00:04:50,050
说咱俩要去啥音乐会
so that we can go to some concert,

42
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:52,070
可你竟连我们来这儿的原因 都不告诉我?
and you won't even tell me why we're here?

43
00:04:52,990 --> 00:04:55,760
没人能告诉你到这儿来的理由 Kate
No one can tell you why you're here, Kate.

44
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:59,730
- 总之我没办法告诉你  - 是你带我来的啊
- Certainly not me.  - You're the one who brought me here.

45
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:01,220
我说的不是教堂
I'm not talking about the church.

46
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:05,200
我是说尘世
I'm talking about here.

47
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,190
你是谁?
Who are you?

48
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,490
你想干嘛?
What do you want?

49
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:13,310
我叫Desmond Hume
My name is Desmond Hume.

50
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:17,510
甚至你可能都没意识到 我是你的朋友
And even though you don't realize it, I'm your friend.

51
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:20,160
至于我想干嘛...
And as for what I want...

52
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,320
我不过是想离开
I want to leave.

53
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,700
离开去哪儿?
Leave and go where?

54
00:05:33,450 --> 00:05:34,160
我带你去看
Let me show you.

55
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,090
你没事吧?
You okay?

56
00:06:09,350 --> 00:06:09,960
嗯
Yeah.

57
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,070
你呢?
You?

58
00:06:14,010 --> 00:06:16,560
说实话 医生 我想知道
Well, to be honest, doc, I'm kinda wondering

59
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:17,710
刚刚到底发生了什么事
what the hell just happened up here.

60
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:20,870
我也想知道呢
That makes two of us.

61
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,860
那你现在是新任Jacob 对么?
So you're the new Jacob, huh?

62
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:29,760
感觉有啥不同?
Feel any different?

63
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:32,300
没啥感觉
Not really.

64
00:06:34,530 --> 00:06:36,600
医生 不如你下山
Well, doc, how about you come down off the mountaintop

65
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:37,830
告诉我们 林子失火
and tell us what the hell the burning bush

66
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:38,960
意味着什么?
had to say for itself?

67
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:43,690
Jacob告诉我 我们得去旧营地的
Jacob told me that we have to go to the bamboo forest

68
00:06:43,850 --> 00:06:45,660
竹林
out past our old camp.

69
00:06:46,370 --> 00:06:47,400
穿过竹林
Just past it, well,

70
00:06:47,730 --> 00:06:49,160
他说 我们就可以找到要保护的地方
he said I'd find the place that we need to protect.

71
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:51,990
那里... 到底是个什么样的地方?
This place... what is it?

72
00:06:52,530 --> 00:06:53,750
他说 它是岛的心脏
He called it the heart of the island.

73
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:55,870
他说 所谓的心脏...
All he said was that it's...

74
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:57,710
就是光
it's a light.

75
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:02,900
而且扮成Locke的烟怪想要扑灭它?
And that Locke smoke thing wants to put it out?

76
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:04,660
嗯 差不多吧
Something like that, yeah.

77
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,130
如果他把光灭了呢?
So what if he does?

78
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:09,380
那我们就玩完了
Then that's it for all of us.

79
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:15,080
但... 如果Locke意在扑灭它 他为啥不去灭?
But... but if Locke wants to put it out, then why hasn't he?

80
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,590
因为他还缺点儿什么
'Cause he ain't got what he needs.

81
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:19,470
我猜 他缺的是Desmond
I'm guessing that'd be Desmond.

82
00:07:20,910 --> 00:07:23,000
所以在你就职之前 这就是我们的目标
That's where we were headed before your inauguration.

83
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:25,890
Sayid说过 Locke把他扔进了一口井
Sayid said Locke tossed him in a well.

84
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:28,210
Jacob没跟我说过任何关于Desmond的事
Jacob didn't say anything to me about Desmond.

85
00:07:28,540 --> 00:07:30,000
他似乎什么也没说过啊
Doesn't sound like he said anything about anything.

86
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:32,060
这倒是真的 他表现得真不像个智者
That's kinda true, dude. He's worse than Yoda.

87
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:36,740
好吧 你们都去岛的心脏地带
All right, y'all head to your heart of the island,

88
00:07:36,910 --> 00:07:39,090
我去抓逃出井的小妖
and I'll go get the magic leprechaun out of that well.

89
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,660
如果我们留下路标 你追得上来么?
If we leave a trail, can you catch up with us?

90
00:07:42,610 --> 00:07:44,750
- 嗯 没问题  - 注意安全
- Hell, yeah, I can.  - Then be safe.

91
00:07:47,150 --> 00:07:48,990
我本想叫你一起去的 不过如果又告诉你
I'd ask you along, but that'd take all the fun

92
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:51,080
- 你不能去 那才叫扫兴  - 呃 我看
- out of me telling you you can't come.  - Uh, I guess

93
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,420
我得拼命克制跟你同去的念头了
I'll just have to resist the urge to follow you anyway.

94
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,720
我有种不祥的预感
I got a bad feeling about this.

95
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:16,720

迷失 第6季第17-18集

96
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:47,850
我不知道你干嘛带我越狱
I don't know why you got me out of prison,

97
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:49,280
也不知道你的目的和身份
what you want or who you are,

98
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:51,550
但你应该知道 我担不起责任...
but you understand I can't be held responsible for...

99
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,300
嗯 嗯 我都明白 兄弟
Yeah, yeah, whatever, dude.

100
00:08:56,710 --> 00:08:58,080
看见这东西 能想起来啥不?
None of this is ringing a bell, is it?

101
00:08:59,220 --> 00:09:01,020
你 我... 麻醉枪?
You, me... tranquilizer gun?

102
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:02,640
你神经病啊
You are insane.

103
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:06,510
好吧 我神经病 你好生在这儿待着
Okay. Fine. I'm insane. Just wait here.

104
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:07,840
要是我不呢?
What if I don't?

105
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:10,210
随你的便
Then that's your choice.

106
00:09:12,130 --> 00:09:13,020
但如果你选择继续跟着我...
But if you stick with me...

107
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:16,340
有朝一日 你会无比庆幸
you'll be happy you did.

108
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:26,440
来了 来了 来了
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

109
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:38,710
我明明挂了"请勿打扰"的标志
"Do no disturb" sign.

110
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:41,810
你是谁?
Who are you?

111
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:45,110
你干嘛笑得像个傻子?
Why you grinnin' like a sodding idiot?

112
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:49,560
呃 你今晚有场音乐会要出演
Uh, you have a concert to perform tonight,

113
00:09:49,650 --> 00:09:50,650
我是来接你的
and I'm here to pick you up.

114
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:53,880
我对Widmore的另一个白痴 说得不够清楚么?
Didn't I make it clear to Widmore's other monkey?

115
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:56,360
我才不在乎什么破音乐会
I don't care about a sodding concert.

116
00:09:57,140 --> 00:09:57,820
Charlie啊...
Charlie...

117
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:00,730
Charlie 如果我告诉你...
Charlie, what if I told you that...

118
00:10:01,770 --> 00:10:04,160
出演这场音乐会
playing this show is

119
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:07,790
将是你人生中最重要的一件事呢?
the most important thing you'll ever do?

120
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:10,300
你会去么?
Would you come then?

121
00:10:13,050 --> 00:10:13,820
滚
Sod off.

122
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:19,020
好吧 兄弟 抱歉了
Okay, dude. Sorry about this.

123
00:10:36,990 --> 00:10:37,640
那是啥?
What was that?

124
00:10:40,070 --> 00:10:40,860
Charlie呗
That was Charlie.

125
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:49,430
你为什么要接手这工作 Jack?
Why did you take the job, Jack?

126
00:10:51,430 --> 00:10:52,390
因为我应该接手
Because I was supposed to.

127
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,530
为什么? 就因为有个陌生人 把我们的名字写在了墙上?
Why? Because some stranger wrote our names on a wall?

128
00:10:58,310 --> 00:11:00,140
我会接手 是因为这个岛是我的唯一
I took it because the island's all I've got left.

129
00:11:01,690 --> 00:11:03,720
它是我这一生 唯一一个我不想毁掉的东西
It's the only thing in my life I haven't managed to ruin.

130
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,120
你什么都没毁啊
You haven't ruined anything.

131
00:11:07,850 --> 00:11:10,100
没有什么是不可挽回的
Nothing is irreversible.

132
00:11:11,730 --> 00:11:13,890
如果我们不是都得死的话 这话听着还真叫人舒心
This would be so sweet if we weren't all about to die.

133
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:34,580
既然你都在旁看着了 那干嘛不一起玩玩?
As long as you're watching, why don't you join us?

134
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:45,410
你到这儿来干嘛 James?
What are you doing here, James?

135
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,470
我听说Desmond落井了
I heard Desmond fell in the well,

136
00:11:47,690 --> 00:11:48,980
所以我来帮忙拉他出来
so I came to help him get out.

137
00:11:53,130 --> 00:11:55,170
看来有人已经抢先我们一步 把他救走了
Looks like somebody beat us both to the punch.

138
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:56,600
哦 真好
Oh, well.

139
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,530
你知道我干嘛到这儿来吗?
Do you know why I'm here?

140
00:11:59,370 --> 00:12:01,410
我猜 你是因为需要Desmond来毁了这个岛
I'm guessing you need Desmond to destroy the island.

141
00:12:03,450 --> 00:12:04,400
答得真准
That's absolutely right.

142
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:07,770
然后呢 烟怪? 和船一起沉了?
Then what, Smokey? You going down with the ship?

143
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,750
自杀貌似不符合你的风格
Suicide doesn't seem like your style.

144
00:12:10,230 --> 00:12:11,470
我不会死的
I'm not going down with anything.

145
00:12:11,990 --> 00:12:15,020
但你和剩下的那些Jacob的小"候选人"
But you and the rest of Jacob's little "candidates"

146
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,240
绝对会死
absolutely are.

147
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:18,350
我们不再是候选人了
We're not candidates anymore.

148
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:20,970
哦! 哦!
Ohh! Oh!

149
00:12:21,310 --> 00:12:21,980
啊
Aah.

150
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,030
再见啦
I'll be seein' ya.

151
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:32,120
你不去追他?
You're not gonna go after him?

152
00:12:34,140 --> 00:12:34,820
不需要
I don't need to.

153
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,840
当你说 你要毁了这个岛的时候
When you said you were gonna destroy the island,

154
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,770
我还以为你是在打比方
I thought you were speaking figuratively.

155
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:42,170
就因为我曾经说过 等我走了 一切由你接管?
Because I said I'd leave you in charge once I was gone?

156
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,930
如果我弄沉了这个岛
I'm sorry if I left out the part

157
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,860
那我得说声抱歉
about the island being on the bottom of the ocean.

158
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,780
换句话说 欢迎你和我一起坐船走
That being said, you're welcome to join me on my boat.

159
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:54,300
因为我们一旦驱使Desmond 做了我们要他做的事
Because once we get Desmond to do what we need him to do,

160
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:57,650
我就坐船离开这个蛮荒之地
I'm gonna sail away from this godforsaken place

161
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:00,070
还要亲眼看着它沉没
and watch it sink.

162
00:13:08,100 --> 00:13:09,330
之前有条狗来过这儿
I think there was a dog here.

163
00:13:20,850 --> 00:13:21,510
早上好
Morning.

164
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:26,920
早上好
Morning.

165
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:27,490
睡得好么?
Sleep okay?

166
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,300
嗯
Aye.

167
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,660
你的帐篷比井底舒服多了
Your camp's a lot nicer than the bottom of a well.

168
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,950
我想我该把这当成是一种赞美
I think I'm gonna go ahead and take that as a compliment.

169
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:38,110
你是要继续对着他喋喋不休
Are you gonna talk his ear off,

170
00:13:38,230 --> 00:13:39,900
还是去给他拿点儿早餐?
or you gonna get the man some breakfast?

171
00:13:40,190 --> 00:13:41,650
我去看看捕鱼机
Guess I'll go check the traps for fish.

172
00:13:44,660 --> 00:13:46,020
走吧 Vincent
Come on. Vincent.

173
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:47,680
我们走
Let's go.

174
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:51,080
呃 Rose 跟我说说...
So, Rose, tell me...

175
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:55,190
你俩在这儿住了多久?
how long have the two of you been living here?

176
00:13:55,880 --> 00:13:58,510
我们75年盖的房子
Well, we built this place in '75,

177
00:13:58,630 --> 00:14:01,460
然后... 住了几年
and... lived here a couple of years,

178
00:14:01,570 --> 00:14:03,640
再然后 一切好转了
and then the sky lit up again.

179
00:14:04,580 --> 00:14:07,670
现在只有上帝知道 我们何时进地狱了
So God only knows when in the hell we are now.

180
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:12,720
所以... Desmond...
So... Desmond...

181
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:14,960
我无心冒犯
