In fact, I'm very curious to meet this mysterious sister

371
00:28:42,890 --> 00:28:46,020
我们结婚那么久 你对她只字未提
you never mentioned the entire time we were married.

372
00:28:46,540 --> 00:28:49,400
我保证你会喜欢她的 她快生了
Well, I'm sure you're gonna love her. She's extremely pregnant.

373
00:28:51,770 --> 00:28:53,600
祝你手术成功 医生
Good luck on your surgery, doctor.

374
00:28:53,980 --> 00:28:54,870
谢谢
Thank you.

375
00:28:55,250 --> 00:28:56,550
- 挑好领带了吗?  - 挑好了
