376
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:57,370
很好
Nice.

377
00:29:04,430 --> 00:29:06,860
嗨 我是洛杉矶警局的Ford探员
Hi. I'm Detective Ford, L.A.P.D.

378
00:29:06,860 --> 00:29:07,450
嗯哼
Mm-hmm.

379
00:29:07,450 --> 00:29:09,620
我要找一间病房... 叫Sun Paik的
I'm looking for a patient's room... Sun Paik.

380
00:29:16,170 --> 00:29:18,320
你不想和大伙儿分享点什么故事吗 医生?
Something you wanna share with the rest of us, doc?

381
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:20,150
指什么?
What's that?

382
00:29:20,810 --> 00:29:22,470
你说过你会杀死Locke的
You said you were gonna kill Locke.

383
00:29:22,470 --> 00:29:26,000
- 你所谓的惊喜是什么?  - Desmond
- What's your surprise?  - Desmond.

384
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:27,620
那有什么用啊?
And how's that gonna work?

385
00:29:28,290 --> 00:29:31,200
我也不知道 我不相信Jacob
I'm not sure yet. I can't believe Jacob

386
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:32,920
会总让他回到这个岛上
would've brought him all the way back to this island

387
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,520
好让Locke利用他毁了这个岛
just so Locke could make him destroy it.

388
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:36,910
- 那又怎么样? Desmond是个诱饵?  - 不
- So what? Desmond's bait?  - No.

389
00:29:37,740 --> 00:29:39,020
我觉得他是件武器
I think he's a weapon.

390
00:29:40,630 --> 00:29:42,640
越听越糊涂了 医生
That's a hell of a long con, doc.

391
00:29:58,400 --> 00:30:00,430
Jack和Desmond...
Jack, Desmond...

392
00:30:01,120 --> 00:30:03,510
这儿只要我们三个人就行了
It should just be the three of us from here on.

393
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:20,780
Jack啊
Jack.

394
00:30:22,290 --> 00:30:23,810
我相信你 哥们
I believe in you, dude.

395
00:30:42,500 --> 00:30:44,020
这竹子要垮了
It's gonna be a bad one.

396
00:31:00,100 --> 00:31:01,630
我们到了
We're here.

397
00:31:17,130 --> 00:31:18,760
这么做无济于事的
This doesn't matter, you know.

398
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:19,960
你说什么?
Excuse me?

399
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:23,470
他要毁了这个岛 你要灭了他...
Him destroying the island, you destroying him...

400
00:31:25,780 --> 00:31:26,830
有什么用呢
It doesn't matter.

401
00:31:29,320 --> 00:31:31,230
你们把我放下去找那束光
I mean, you're gonna lower me into that light,

402
00:31:31,540 --> 00:31:33,050
我会去另一个地方...
and I'm gonna go somewhere else...

403
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:37,170
在那儿 我们可以和喜欢的人待在一起
a place where we can be with the ones that we love

404
00:31:37,950 --> 00:31:40,000
不用再考虑这个该死的岛了
and not have to ever think about this damn island again.

405
00:31:42,870 --> 00:31:44,660
你知道最精彩的部分吗 Jack?
And you know the best part, Jack?

406
00:31:45,580 --> 00:31:46,270
是什么?
What?

407
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,730
你也在那儿
You're in this place.

408
00:31:51,250 --> 00:31:54,790
我们在大洋航空815航班上相邻而坐
You know, we sat next to each other on Oceanic 815.

409
00:31:58,150 --> 00:31:59,400
不曾坠毁
It never crashed.

410
00:31:59,730 --> 00:32:01,230
我们互相交谈
We spoke to each other.

411
00:32:01,990 --> 00:32:03,160
你看起来很高兴
You seemed happy.

412
00:32:06,070 --> 00:32:08,680
或许我也有办法 把你带去那儿
You know, maybe I can find a way to bring you there, too.

413
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:11,920
Desmond 我尝试过一次
Desmond, I tried that once.

414
00:32:13,030 --> 00:32:14,990
没有捷径 也无法重新来过
There are no shortcuts, no do-overs.

415
00:32:14,990 --> 00:32:17,750
事情发生了就是发生了 相信我 我知道的
What happened, happened. Trust me, I know.

416
00:32:19,370 --> 00:32:20,870
我们所做的很有意义
All of this matters.

417
00:32:23,510 --> 00:32:24,440
要继续吗?
Shall we?

418
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:01,380
我们待这儿干嘛呀?
What are we doing here?

419
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:04,880
别人不让我告诉你
I'm not allowed to tell you.

420
00:33:05,630 --> 00:33:07,700
什么叫"别人不让"啊?
What do you mean, you're "not allowed"?

421
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:09,600
要守规矩的 哥们
There are rules, dude.

422
00:33:09,790 --> 00:33:11,000
谁定的规矩?
Whose rules?

423
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:13,610
不用担心 相信我就行了 没问题吧?
Don't worry about it. Just trust me, okay?

424
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:17,500
我相信你
I trust you.

425
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:21,670
我能问问 是什么让你这么相信我吗?
And what, may I ask, have I done to deserve your trust?

426
00:33:23,410 --> 00:33:25,450
我觉得你是个好人 Sayid
I think you're a good guy, Sayid.

427
00:33:27,170 --> 00:33:29,330
我知道 很多人说你是个坏人
I know a lot of people have told you that you're not.

428
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:32,090
可能你听多了
Maybe you've heard it so many times

429
00:33:32,090 --> 00:33:33,360
也就信了
you started believing it.

430
00:33:35,320 --> 00:33:37,730
但你不能让别人来告诉你 你是怎样的人 哥们
But you can't let other people tell you what you are, dude.

431
00:33:38,460 --> 00:33:40,230
这得靠你自己来决定
You have to decide that for yourself.

432
00:33:42,190 --> 00:33:43,180
对不起
I'm sorry.

433
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:47,610
你显然对我一无所知
You clearly don't know anything about me.

434
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:50,840
我知道你很多事情 哥们
I know a lot about you, dude.

435
00:34:02,280 --> 00:34:03,880
看起来像是一顿暴打
Looks like a gnarly fight.

436
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,460
嘿 放开我弟弟!
Hey, leave my brother alone!

437
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:28,830
嘿 没事儿了
Hey, it's all right.

438
00:34:55,620 --> 00:34:57,310
Sayid啊
Sayid.

439
00:34:58,330 --> 00:34:59,760
Shannon啊
Shannon.

440
00:35:06,770 --> 00:35:08,860
我刚挨了顿揍 哥们
I just got pounded, man.

441
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:11,150
谢谢你抽空来
Thanks for taking your sweet time.

442
00:35:11,490 --> 00:35:12,980
很乐意为你效劳
It takes as long as it takes.

443
00:35:15,130 --> 00:35:18,130
把她从澳大利亚带回来真让人讨厌
It was a pain in the ass getting her here from Australia.

444
00:35:18,130 --> 00:35:20,600
没错 但是 哥们你知道么? 这很值哦
Yeah. But, dude? It was worth it.

445
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:27,000
我应该上去打个招呼吗?
Should I go get 'em?

446
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:30,810
别 让他们单独待一会儿吧
Nah. Let's give 'em a minute.

447
00:35:44,750 --> 00:35:46,570
Linus 听得到吗?
Linus, are you there?

448
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:49,750
那是什么玩意儿?
What the hell's that?

449
00:35:50,020 --> 00:35:51,450
Miles 你在哪儿?
Miles, where are you?

450
00:35:51,460 --> 00:35:53,160
我们刚到九头蛇岛
We just got to Hydra Island.

451
00:35:53,160 --> 00:35:55,490
- 我们正往飞机那儿赶  - Miles 听我说
- We're on our way to the plane.  - Miles, listen to me.

452
00:35:55,490 --> 00:35:57,330
- 无论你做什么 都不要炸掉那架飞机!  - 我们不会炸掉它的
- Whatever you do, don't blow up that plane!  - We're not gonna blow it up.

453
00:35:57,330 --> 00:35:59,680
我们要乘着它离开这个岛
We're gonna fly it the hell off the island.

454
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:03,860
- 快过来吧!  - 搞什么鬼啊?
- Just get over here now!  - What in the hell?

455
00:36:07,560 --> 00:36:08,670
Claire啊
Claire.

456
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:12,530
Miles 我是Kate 你刚是说"Claire"吗?
Miles, it's Kate. Did you say "Claire"?

457
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,200
她还好吗?
Is she okay?

458
00:36:15,170 --> 00:36:16,440
把枪放下
Put the gun down.

459
00:36:21,260 --> 00:36:22,870
不要靠近!
Don't come any closer!

460
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:24,510
Miles啊
Miles?

461
00:36:25,630 --> 00:36:27,270
Miles 发生什么事了?
Miles, what happened?

462
00:36:27,550 --> 00:36:28,950
Miles 听得到吗?
Miles, are you there?

463
00:36:28,950 --> 00:36:30,790
是他派你来杀我的 对吧?
He sent you to kill me, didn't he?

464
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:32,680
不是 我们跟Locke不是一伙的
No, listen. We're not with Locke.

465
00:36:33,590 --> 00:36:35,160
我凭什么相信你?
Why should I believe you?

466
00:36:35,160 --> 00:36:38,300
因为我们有机会可以离他远远的了
Because we have a real chance to get far, far away from him.

467
00:36:38,670 --> 00:36:41,360
我们终于能摆脱他的魔爪了
We can be free of everything he ever did to us

468
00:36:41,370 --> 00:36:42,620
再也不用回来了
and never look back.

469
00:36:45,940 --> 00:36:47,380
我们可以回家了
We can go home.

470
00:36:53,530 --> 00:36:54,920
要和我们一起走吗 Claire?
Will you come with us, Claire?

471
00:36:58,700 --> 00:36:59,590
不
No.

472
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:14,780
好吧 我们...
All right, we...

473
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:17,800
我们轻轻地把他放下去
we lower him down nice and easy.

474
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:20,190
你知道一到下面就该做什么了吧?
You know what to do once you get down there?

475
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:20,940
知道
Aye.

476
00:37:22,750 --> 00:37:24,580
我要去最亮的那束光那儿
I'll go where the light's brightest.

477
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:27,590
不要挂了哦
Don't get yourself killed.

478
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:53,860
这让你想起些什么了吧 Jack?
This remind you of anything, Jack?

479
00:37:55,270 --> 00:37:56,180
什么?
What?

480
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,220
Desmond啊...
Desmond...

481
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:02,580
穿过下面那个洞
Going down into a hole in the ground.

482
00:38:03,890 --> 00:38:05,530
如果那儿有个按钮
If there was a button down there to push,

483
00:38:05,530 --> 00:38:07,450
我们再争论要不要去按
we could fight about whether or not to push it.

484
00:38:09,810 --> 00:38:11,140
就像以前那样
It'd be just like old times.

485
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:14,020
你不是John Locke
You're not John Locke.

486
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:18,820
你套着他的皮囊 这是对他记忆的亵渎
You disrespect his memory by wearing his face,

487
00:38:18,820 --> 00:38:20,270
你和他分明就是两个人
but you're nothing like him.

488
00:38:21,770 --> 00:38:23,870
结果证明他都是对的
Turns out he was right about most everything.

489
00:38:24,570 --> 00:38:27,480
我多么希望 我能在他活着的时候 告诉他这些啊
I just wish I could've told him that while he was still alive.

490
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:30,890
他的想法都是错的 Jack
He wasn't right about anything, Jack.

491
00:38:31,930 --> 00:38:33,190
当这个岛
And when this island

492
00:38:33,730 --> 00:38:36,260
沉到海底的时候 当你和岛一起沉下去的时候
drops into the ocean, and you drop with it,

493
00:38:36,850 --> 00:38:38,460
那会儿你就会明白了
you're finally gonna realize that.

494
00:38:41,640 --> 00:38:45,460
好吧 那就让我们看看 到底谁是对的吧
Well, we'll just have to see which one of us is right, then.

495
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:22,870
哦
Oh.

496
00:39:24,090 --> 00:39:25,440
是医院打来的
It's the hospital.

497
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:27,270
去吧 我猜肯定是要紧事
Go ahead. I'm sure it's important.

498
00:39:27,270 --> 00:39:31,030
- 对不起 我尽力赶回来  - 我知道 没事儿 去吧
- I am so sorry. I will be back as soon as I can.  - I know. It's cool. Go.

499
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:33,960
- 希望下次能更进一步互相了解 好么?  - 好的 一定
- We'll get to know each other better, I hope?  - Okay. Yeah. Yeah, yeah, for sure.

500
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:38,930
我 呃 我想就只剩我和你了吧 孩子
Well, I, uh, I guess it's just you and me, kid.

501
00:39:44,790 --> 00:39:45,890
喂
Oy.

502
00:39:47,690 --> 00:39:48,560
醒醒
Wake up.

503
00:39:48,900 --> 00:39:50,460
醒醒 快啊 醒醒
Wake up. Come on. Wake up.

504
00:39:52,930 --> 00:39:53,830
你在干嘛?
What are you doin'?

505
00:39:53,830 --> 00:39:55,690
我只是根据指示办事
I'm just following the instructions.

506
00:39:56,410 --> 00:39:57,710
你是乐队里的吧?
You're in the band, aren't you?

507
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,290
你怎么知道的?
How do you know that?

508
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:04,920

贝斯手 演出的时候叫醒我

509
00:40:06,890 --> 00:40:08,940
我被一个肥仔打了一枪
I was shot by a fat man.

510
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:11,440
没事
It's all right.

511
00:40:14,570 --> 00:40:15,490
打扰一下
Excuse me.

512
00:40:17,410 --> 00:40:19,360
嘿 打扰一下 你知道乐队在哪儿吗?
Hey, excuse me. Do you know where the band is?

513
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:24,730
抱歉 呃 能再说一遍吗?
I'm sorry. Uh, pardon me?

514
00:40:25,110 --> 00:40:26,820
我... 我想他是乐队里的吧
I... I think he's in the band.

515
00:40:28,590 --> 00:40:30,960
是的 没错 当然了
Yes, yes. Of course.

516
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:33,750
他是"驱动轴"乐队的贝斯手
He's the bass player from Drive Shaft.

517
00:40:34,070 --> 00:40:35,680
今晚他们为我伴奏
They're accompanying me tonight.

518
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:37,390
由我来弹钢琴
I play piano.

519
00:40:39,410 --> 00:40:42,270
我叫Daniel 全名Daniel Widmore
I'm Daniel. Daniel Widmore.

520
00:40:43,330 --> 00:40:44,380
我叫Charlotte
I'm Charlotte.

521
00:40:44,950 --> 00:40:47,220
很高兴见到你 Charlotte
It's a great pleasure to meet you, Charlotte.

522
00:40:47,900 --> 00:40:48,970
我也是
You, too.

523
00:40:53,620 --> 00:40:55,230
请带路吧
Well, lead the way.

524
00:40:58,550 --> 00:41:00,320
打扰一下 这是23号桌吗?
Excuse me. Is this Table 23?

525
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:02,750
是的 没错
Aye. Indeed it is.

526
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:06,270
Claire啊
Claire?

527
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:10,620
你们俩认识?
You two know each other?

528
00:41:10,950 --> 00:41:12,690
女士们 先生们 晚上好
Good evening, ladies and gentlemen.

529
00:41:12,690 --> 00:41:14,340
请朝这边看 可以吗?
May I have your attention, please?

530
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:19,050
