532
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:24,410
我是Pierre Chang博士
I'm Dr. Pierre Chang.

533
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:26,550
谢谢
Thank you.

534
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:31,020
我想今晚对于我们来说意义非凡
I think we have quite a special evening ahead of us.

535
00:41:31,020 --> 00:41:33,030
所以接下来我们直奔主题吧 好么?
So let's get to it, shall we?

536
00:41:33,780 --> 00:41:35,040
我很荣幸
It is my pleasure

537
00:41:35,040 --> 00:41:37,780
向大家介绍Daniel Widmore先生
to introduce you to Mr. Daniel Widmore,

538
00:41:37,780 --> 00:41:40,070
以及"驱动轴"乐队
accompanied by Drive Shaft.

539
00:42:39,540 --> 00:42:40,740
你还好吗?
You okay?

540
00:42:41,070 --> 00:42:43,990
没事 没事 我只是... 要去下洗手间
Yeah. Yeah, I'm just... I'm just gonna use the bathroom.

541
00:42:43,990 --> 00:42:45,190
我... 我去去就来
I'll... I'll be right back.

542
00:45:06,750 --> 00:45:07,790
不!
No!

543
00:45:08,300 --> 00:45:09,780
不!
No!

544
00:45:14,370 --> 00:45:16,100
好像...
It looks like...

545
00:45:16,720 --> 00:45:17,890
你搞错了
you were wrong.

546
00:45:21,600 --> 00:45:22,770
再见了 Jack
Good-bye, Jack.

547
00:45:47,830 --> 00:45:49,620
好像你也搞错了
Looks like you were wrong, too.

548
00:46:13,700 --> 00:46:15,280
嗯 有人吗?
Um, hello?

549
00:46:15,920 --> 00:46:16,790
有人吗?
Hello?

550
00:46:18,190 --> 00:46:21,880
嗨 嗯 请问洗手间在哪? 啊! 噢!
Hi. Uh, do you know where the bathroom is? Mm! Ohh!

551
00:46:25,630 --> 00:46:27,260
啊 可以去找医生来吗?
Uh, can you please get a doctor?

552
00:46:29,070 --> 00:46:30,290
世界很小 对吧?
