别这样
No.

934
01:22:07,990 --> 01:22:09,420
我们没时间了!
We're running out of time!

935
01:22:15,250 --> 01:22:18,510
- Jim 总是在最后一秒见到你  - 我也很高兴见到你 Enos
- Way to wait till the last second, Jim.  - Good to see you, too, Enos.

936
01:22:18,580 --> 01:22:19,370
他们上来了!
We got 'em!

937
01:22:19,480 --> 01:22:21,170
各位 系紧安全带!
Everybody, buckle up tight!

938
01:22:22,080 --> 01:22:22,990
抓住了!
Hold on!

939
01:22:31,870 --> 01:22:32,880
Frank 我们上路吧
Here we go, Frank.

940
01:23:00,720 --> 01:23:01,580
拜托
Come on.

941
01:23:04,280 --> 01:23:05,130
起飞吧
Come on.

942
01:23:21,230 --> 01:23:22,000
上帝保佑
Amen.

943
01:24:39,920 --> 01:24:42,460
他成功了 光又回来了
He did it. The light's back on.

944
01:24:42,720 --> 01:24:43,820
哥们儿 拉
Dude, pull.

945
01:24:48,900 --> 01:24:50,580
坚持住 Jack!
Hang on, Jack!

946
01:25:02,590 --> 01:25:03,450
拉上来了!
Got him!

947
01:25:05,490 --> 01:25:06,340
Desmond啊
Desmond?

948
01:25:06,970 --> 01:25:07,700
不是吧
No.

949
01:25:08,940 --> 01:25:09,830
Jack啊
Jack!

950
01:25:17,490 --> 01:25:18,910
Jack啊
Jack!

951
01:26:17,300 --> 01:26:18,440
你好 Benjamin
Hello, Benjamin.

952
01:26:21,450 --> 01:26:22,390
你好 John
Hello, John.

953
01:26:25,240 --> 01:26:26,830
大家都在里面吗?
Is everyone already inside?

954
01:26:28,690 --> 01:26:31,040
是的 大多数都在
I believe most of them are, yes.

955
01:26:31,670 --> 01:26:32,820
嗯
Mm.

956
01:26:35,880 --> 01:26:37,770
很抱歉 我曾那样对你 John
I'm very sorry for what I did to you, John.

957
01:26:41,640 --> 01:26:42,780
我很自私
I was selfish

958
01:26:43,640 --> 01:26:44,430
很嫉妒你
and jealous.

959
01:26:45,820 --> 01:26:47,480
我想得到你所拥有的一切
I wanted everything you had.

960
01:26:51,390 --> 01:26:52,310
我有什么?
What did I have?

961
01:26:55,000 --> 01:26:56,330
你很特殊 John
You were special, John.

962
01:26:58,950 --> 01:26:59,790
而我很平凡
And I wasn't.

963
01:27:04,390 --> 01:27:05,960
呃 Ben 如果有用的话
Well, if it helps, Ben,

964
01:27:06,690 --> 01:27:07,490
我原谅你
I forgive you.

965
01:27:11,840 --> 01:27:12,780
谢谢你 John
Thank you, John.

966
01:27:14,210 --> 01:27:15,050
那确实很有帮助
That does help.

967
01:27:18,060 --> 01:27:20,230
是言语所无法表达的
It matters more than I can say.

968
01:27:22,510 --> 01:27:23,680
那你现在要做什么?
What are you gonna do now?

969
01:27:24,660 --> 01:27:26,630
我还有些事情要处理
I have some things that I still need to work out.

970
01:27:27,120 --> 01:27:30,370
我可能会再待一会儿
I think I'll stay here a while.

971
01:27:34,470 --> 01:27:36,820
你知道吗 我觉得你不用再待在轮椅里了
You know, I don't think you need to be in that chair anymore.

972
01:28:01,670 --> 01:28:02,540
Ben 再见
Good-bye, Ben.

973
01:28:47,320 --> 01:28:49,440
Desmond会好起来的
I think Desmond's gonna be okay.

974
01:28:54,760 --> 01:28:56,170
Jack... 走了
Jack's... gone.

975
01:28:59,320 --> 01:29:00,160
对吗?
Isn't he?

976
01:29:10,970 --> 01:29:12,800
这是他的职责 Hugo
He did his job, Hugo.

977
01:29:14,320 --> 01:29:15,350
现在是我的职责了
It's my job now.

978
01:29:18,930 --> 01:29:20,280
我到底应该做什么?
What the hell am I supposed to do?

979
01:29:23,440 --> 01:29:25,570
我觉得你要做你擅长的
I think you do what you do best.

980
01:29:28,290 --> 01:29:29,240
照顾大伙儿
Take care of people.

981
01:29:32,910 --> 01:29:34,900
你可以从帮助Desmond回家开始
You can start by helping Desmond get home.

982
01:29:35,910 --> 01:29:36,740
但要怎么做?
But how?

983
01:29:38,780 --> 01:29:39,410
人们不能离开这座岛
People can't leave the island.

984
01:29:40,580 --> 01:29:42,450
那是Jacob规定的
That's how Jacob ran things.

985
01:29:43,870 --> 01:29:45,100
也许有别的方法
Maybe there's another way.

986
01:29:47,490 --> 01:29:48,270
一个更好的方法
A better way.

987
01:29:51,880 --> 01:29:52,760
你会帮我吗?
Will you help me?

988
01:29:54,910 --> 01:29:55,680
你说什么?
I'm sorry?

989
01:29:56,880 --> 01:30:00,910
我可以招一些人 比如... 有经验的人
I could really use someone with, like... experience

990
01:30:00,980 --> 01:30:02,110
就一段时间
for a little while.

991
01:30:07,320 --> 01:30:08,390
Ben 你会帮我吗?
Will you help me, Ben?

992
01:30:12,720 --> 01:30:13,730
荣幸之至
I'd be honored.

993
01:30:18,170 --> 01:30:18,990
太棒了
Cool.

994
01:30:33,230 --> 01:30:35,150
哦! 嘿 哥们儿
Oh! Hey, dude.

995
01:30:36,270 --> 01:30:37,560
你好 Hugo
Hello, Hugo.

996
01:30:38,260 --> 01:30:39,220
我们都在里面
We're all inside.

997
01:30:41,590 --> 01:30:42,990
我不想进去
I don't think I'm coming in.

998
01:30:50,750 --> 01:30:51,570
你知道...
You know...

999
01:30:53,170 --> 01:30:55,380
你是个很好的二把手
you were a real good Number Two.

1000
01:30:57,010 --> 01:30:59,950
你也是个很出色的一把手 Hugo
And you were a great Number One, Hugo.

1001
01:31:02,030 --> 01:31:02,930
谢谢 哥们儿
Thanks, dude.

1002
01:31:04,560 --> 01:31:05,400
一会儿见
I'll see you.

1003
01:31:24,450 --> 01:31:25,430
你知道我们在哪儿吗?
Do you know where we are?

1004
01:31:27,490 --> 01:31:29,460
这是应该为我父亲举办葬礼的地方
This is where I was gonna have my father's funeral.

1005
01:31:32,110 --> 01:31:33,820
他死在了澳大利亚
He died in Australia.

1006
01:31:35,760 --> 01:31:36,550
很抱歉
I'm sorry.

1007
01:31:40,160 --> 01:31:41,400
为什么带我来这?
Why did you bring me here?

1008
01:31:43,890 --> 01:31:44,630
因为这里将是
Because this is where

1009
01:31:44,680 --> 01:31:47,060
为你父亲举办葬礼的地方
you are gonna have your father's funeral.

1010
01:31:51,620 --> 01:31:53,130
你可以在后面逛逛
You can go in around back.

1011
01:31:53,570 --> 01:31:55,480
等等 你... 你去哪?
Wait. W... where are you going?

1012
01:31:56,280 --> 01:31:57,100
里面
Inside.

1013
01:31:59,130 --> 01:32:00,380
我在那等你...
I'll be waiting for you there...

1014
01:32:01,620 --> 01:32:02,550
等你准备好
once you're ready.

1015
01:32:05,890 --> 01:32:06,830
准备好什么?
Ready for what?

1016
01:32:10,310 --> 01:32:11,150
离开
To leave.

1017
01:35:28,640 --> 01:35:29,730
嘿 孩子
Hey, kiddo.

1018
01:35:40,880 --> 01:35:41,720
爸爸?
Dad?

1019
01:35:44,250 --> 01:35:45,310
你好 Jack
Hello, Jack.

1020
01:35:49,040 --> 01:35:50,370
我不明白
I don't understand.

1021
01:35:53,220 --> 01:35:54,140
你死了
You died.

1022
01:35:55,380 --> 01:35:56,200
对
Yeah.

1023
01:35:57,020 --> 01:35:58,090
是的 我死了
Yes, I did.

1024
01:36:01,230 --> 01:36:03,580
那你怎么又在这儿?
Then how are you here right now?

1025
01:36:08,050 --> 01:36:09,350
那你怎么在这儿?
How are you here?

1026
01:36:25,040 --> 01:36:26,330
我也死了
I died, too.

1027
01:36:34,030 --> 01:36:35,020
没事儿的
It's okay.

1028
01:36:35,950 --> 01:36:37,020
没事儿
It's okay.

1029
01:36:37,910 --> 01:36:39,000
没关系的 儿子
It's okay, son.

1030
01:36:55,660 --> 01:36:57,370
我爱你 爸爸
I love you, dad.

1031
01:36:57,460 --> 01:36:59,030
我也爱你 儿子
I love you, too, son.

1032
01:37:01,450 --> 01:37:02,230
你...
Are you...

1033
01:37:04,570 --> 01:37:05,400
你是真的吗?
Are you real?

1034
01:37:07,450 --> 01:37:09,300
希望是
I sure hope so.

1035
01:37:11,060 --> 01:37:12,270
是的 我是真的
Yeah, I'm real.

1036
01:37:12,990 --> 01:37:13,960
你是真的
You're real.

1037
01:37:14,460 --> 01:37:16,940
你发生过的每一件事都是真的
Everything that's ever happened to you is real.

1038
01:37:17,750 --> 01:37:19,360
在教堂里面的所有人...
All those people in the church...

1039
01:37:20,150 --> 01:37:21,440
也都是真的
they're all real, too.

1040
01:37:22,670 --> 01:37:23,660
他们都...
They're all...

1041
01:37:24,740 --> 01:37:25,790
他们都死了?
they're all dead?

1042
01:37:29,070 --> 01:37:31,040
每个人都会死 孩子
Everyone dies sometime, kiddo.

1043
01:37:35,800 --> 01:37:37,590
有些人死在你前面 有些...
Some of them before you, some...

1044
01:37:38,420 --> 01:37:39,520
死在你后面
long after you.

1045
01:37:41,730 --> 01:37:43,280
但他们怎么现在都在?
But why are they all here now?

1046
01:37:45,660 --> 01:37:49,380
呃 在这里没有"现在"
Well, there is no "now" here.

1047
01:38:02,440 --> 01:38:03,510
我们在哪儿 爸爸?
Where are we, dad?

1048
01:38:06,200 --> 01:38:08,870
这是个... 你们能聚在一起的地方
This is a place that you... that you all made together

1049
01:38:08,940 --> 01:38:11,080
这样 你能找到其他人
so that you could find one another.

1050
01:38:18,680 --> 01:38:21,540
你生命中最重要的一段日子
The most important part of your life

1051
01:38:22,330 --> 01:38:24,630
就是和他们共同度过的时光
was the time that you spent with these people.

1052
01:38:26,550 --> 01:38:28,310
这就是为什么你们都在这里
That's why all of you are here.

1053
01:38:29,420 --> 01:38:31,210
Jack 没有人能独自度过这段时光
Nobody does it alone, Jack.

1054
01:38:32,810 --> 01:38:34,020
你需要他们每一个人
You needed all of them,

1055
01:38:35,170 --> 01:38:36,140
同样 他们也需要你
and they needed you.

1056
01:38:39,820 --> 01:38:40,770
需要我干什么?
For what?

1057
01:38:44,730 --> 01:38:45,670
怀念
To remember.

1058
01:38:49,280 --> 01:38:51,460
还有... 放手
And to... let go.

1059
01:38:58,380 --> 01:38:59,280
Kate啊...
Kate...

1060
01:39:00,380 --> 01:39:01,550
她说我们要离开
she said we were leaving.

1061
01:39:02,760 --> 01:39:04,200
不是离开 不是
Not leave. No.

1062
01:39:07,640 --> 01:39:08,480
是继续生活
Moving on.

1063
01:39:15,100 --> 01:39:16,000
我们要去哪儿?
Where are we going?

1064
01:39:21,260 --> 01:39:22,340
让我们去找找看吧
Let's go find out.

1065
01:40:02,400 --> 01:40:04,790
我们都在等你呢
We've been waitin' for ya.

1066
01:40:20,000 --> 01:40:25,200

迷失 全剧终 谢谢观赏

